## 3. Results

### 3.1 Model Performance on B3DB Test Set

| Model | AUC-ROC | AUC-PR | Accuracy | F1 | Brier Score |
|-------|---------|--------|----------|----|-------------|
| **Random Forest (calibrated)** | **0.9617** | **0.9757** | **0.884** | **0.912** | **0.082** |
| Logistic Regression (calibrated) | 0.9109 | 0.9345 | 0.862 | 0.890 | 0.128 |
| GNN AttentiveFP (Colab GPU) | 0.910 | — | — | — | — |
| DeepChem RF baseline | 0.868 | — | — | — | — |

The calibrated Random Forest achieved AUC-ROC of 0.9617 (+9.2% vs DeepChem baseline).
The Brier score of 0.082 indicates well-calibrated probability estimates.

### 3.2 Benchmark Validation on 15 Curated Molecules

