| Morphine | BBB+ | **BBB+** | 0.928 | 6/6 | High |
| Atropine | BBB+ | **BBB+** | 0.846 | 6/6 | Moderate |
| Dopamine | Borderline | **Borderline** | 0.697 | 6/6 | Low |
| Serotonin | Borderline | **Borderline** | 0.691 | 6/6 | Low |
| L-DOPA | Borderline | **Borderline** | 0.466 | 4/6 | Low |
| Gabapentin | Borderline | **Borderline** | 0.727 | 6/6 | Low |
| Ampicillin | BBB- | **BBB-** | 0.343 | 4/6 | Moderate |
